# [TSVWG](../wg/tsvwg.html)

## Summary

The TSVWG working group met to discuss several active and proposed transport drafts. Key topics included progress and interoperability testing of SCTP DTLS Chunk, alternative proposals for DTLS key management, updates on FQ-PIE, deployment experiences with L4S and mobile L4S, and optimizations for the WebRTC SCTP handshake. While some documents are nearing Working Group Last Call (WGLC), others face open questions regarding scope, design paths, or IESG discusses that the group is actively working to resolve.

